WEBVTT

00:00.804 --> 00:01.998
<i>(Carrie)</i>
<i>Before there was sex...</i>

00:02.118 --> 00:04.796
<i>Before there was the city,</i>
<i>there was just me,</i>

00:04.916 --> 00:07.803
<i>Carrie... Carrie Bradshaw</i>
<i>from Castlebury, Connecticut.</i>

00:07.923 --> 00:09.823
You seriously didn't have
to come see me off.

00:09.825 --> 00:10.957
I'm crazy about you.

00:10.959 --> 00:12.025
I'm Samantha.

00:12.027 --> 00:13.460
I'm having sex with your husband.
(Crying)

00:13.462 --> 00:14.661
Feels like you haven't totally

00:14.663 --> 00:15.996
worked out
the open marriage thing.

00:15.998 --> 00:18.098
I like you, which means
I don't wanna share you.

00:18.100 --> 00:20.233
You're engaged? To who?
To Harlan.

00:20.235 --> 00:21.968
You have a job
at “Interview” Magazine.

00:21.970 --> 00:23.570
But I'm going to N.Y.U.
in the fall.

00:23.572 --> 00:25.372
Why waste four years
in order to get a job

00:25.374 --> 00:26.706
that you've already been given?

00:26.708 --> 00:28.341
Take the job.
You were born to write.

00:28.343 --> 00:29.943
You always were wonderful
with words.

00:29.945 --> 00:31.278
You are throwing away college.

00:31.280 --> 00:33.113
And if you get fired,
what will you do then?

00:33.115 --> 00:34.814
- Well, I don't know but...
- What <i>do</i> you know?

00:34.816 --> 00:36.182
I know that I'm taking the job!

00:36.184 --> 00:37.651
I need to
follow my dreams, too.

00:37.653 --> 00:38.718
I'm going to California.

00:38.720 --> 00:39.786
(Bottles clink)

00:39.788 --> 00:40.887
Thank you
for being here for me.

00:40.889 --> 00:43.023
Of course. Always.

